WEBVTT

00:10.600 --> 00:12.000
[Respect Copyright, Everyone's Responsibility]

01:06.540 --> 01:08.000
[The Eternal Fragrance]

01:08.000 --> 01:11.980
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

01:12.020 --> 01:15.140
[Episode 27]

01:18.030 --> 01:19.500
It ends like this again.

01:21.080 --> 01:21.810
Is this

01:22.270 --> 01:23.530
truly the end?

01:46.830 --> 01:47.450
Zhaomin.

01:50.750 --> 01:52.010
The detox pill I just gave you

01:52.080 --> 01:53.060
is for countering demonic energy.

01:53.310 --> 01:55.170
It should be working by now.

01:55.600 --> 01:56.250
Any more left?

01:57.000 --> 01:57.620
No.

01:58.160 --> 02:00.340
I only got two from Elder Dongyang.

02:00.720 --> 02:02.170
Too bad he's not here.

02:02.190 --> 02:02.890
What do we do now?

02:05.880 --> 02:07.060
Let's find Master and the others.

02:15.670 --> 02:16.220
You go ahead.

02:16.480 --> 02:17.370
I'm going to save Lifei.

02:17.670 --> 02:18.250
You...

02:21.670 --> 02:22.220
Fine.

02:22.550 --> 02:23.780
Zhaomin, be careful.

02:24.040 --> 02:24.940
Don't draw any attention.

02:24.960 --> 02:25.900
Wait until our backup arrives.

02:25.990 --> 02:26.460
Got it.

02:27.760 --> 02:28.340
Zhaomin.

02:29.800 --> 02:30.370
What is it?

02:33.590 --> 02:34.500
We'll talk later.

02:34.520 --> 02:35.180
Just go save them.

02:47.920 --> 02:48.650
Will you submit or not

02:49.830 --> 02:50.780
Huolian Abbey

02:50.960 --> 02:52.570
will never side with demons!

03:15.590 --> 03:16.180
You.

03:17.150 --> 03:17.740
Come here!

03:20.760 --> 03:23.180
Qiongqi, come at me!

03:23.390 --> 03:23.970
Master!

03:26.150 --> 03:27.130
Hang in there!

03:35.760 --> 03:36.370
Watch out!

03:49.270 --> 03:50.060
You're finally here!

04:01.200 --> 04:03.410
Where did you hide the Lei Xiuyuan

04:04.320 --> 04:05.650
who promised never to hurt me?

04:31.350 --> 04:31.980
Lifei.

04:33.880 --> 04:34.810
I will never hurt you.

04:42.640 --> 04:44.330
Lei Xiuyuan, let Lifei go!

05:00.030 --> 05:00.940
Zhaomin.

05:05.350 --> 05:06.130
Zhaomin!

05:09.000 --> 05:09.740
You're not him.

05:11.080 --> 05:11.860
You're not him.

05:13.270 --> 05:14.250
You are Yecha!

05:14.680 --> 05:15.890
You are Yecha!

05:28.680 --> 05:30.890
Lifei, forgive me.

05:32.150 --> 05:33.540
Only by breaking through your seals

05:34.710 --> 05:36.250
can I truly protect you.

06:58.590 --> 06:59.660
You've fully shed your shell.

07:01.470 --> 07:03.180
No one can ever hurt you again.

07:04.680 --> 07:05.420
Not even me.

08:10.710 --> 08:11.420
This time,

08:13.200 --> 08:14.300
I kept my word.

08:16.100 --> 08:19.790
♪The warmth within my arms♪

08:20.170 --> 08:23.210
♪I can no longer hold on to♪

08:23.510 --> 08:26.910
♪In the cold night, how can I♪

08:27.080 --> 08:27.890
Xiuyuan.

08:27.890 --> 08:30.540
♪Keep you warm until sunrise?♪

08:30.910 --> 08:34.110
♪My heartbeat freezes♪

08:34.430 --> 08:37.630
♪I can no longer tell you♪

08:38.030 --> 08:41.230
♪Looking you in the eyes, I cannot♪

08:41.510 --> 08:44.550
♪Utter that line♪

08:44.910 --> 08:46.630
♪Knowing love and hate♪

08:46.950 --> 08:50.870
♪Pain and wounds cannot be stopped♪

08:52.230 --> 08:53.830
♪I still linger on♪

08:54.230 --> 08:58.430
♪Unwilling to let go of every inch of our past♪

08:58.830 --> 09:03.190
♪Last night's stars cast faint glimmers♪

09:03.470 --> 09:06.430
♪But we thought nothing of it♪

09:06.750 --> 09:10.190
♪With a heartbroken cry♪

09:10.550 --> 09:13.670
♪I wish you well♪

09:13.990 --> 09:15.670
♪Knowing right and wrong♪

09:16.030 --> 09:19.160
♪Black and gray are all illusions♪

09:19.160 --> 09:19.780
No.

09:21.310 --> 09:22.950
♪You're still screaming♪

09:23.230 --> 09:26.560
♪Running relentlessly without regret♪

09:26.560 --> 09:27.380
No!

09:27.990 --> 09:32.230
♪The storm looms, yet the wind stands in its way♪

09:32.590 --> 09:34.510
♪A final farewell left on the cliff♪

09:34.510 --> 09:35.610
No!

09:35.750 --> 09:42.240
♪Leaping straight into that heartbreaking past♪

09:42.680 --> 09:46.680
♪Just to keep you safe♪

09:51.080 --> 09:54.690
♪My breath is about to stop♪

09:54.810 --> 09:58.330
♪Those hands can no longer hold yours♪

09:58.450 --> 10:01.890
♪Through the future snow, wind, and fog♪

10:02.050 --> 10:04.840
♪Who will be there by your side?♪

10:05.240 --> 10:06.630
♪I smile as it ends♪

10:06.630 --> 10:08.940
No! No!

10:09.040 --> 10:12.440
♪Afraid that you might cry for me♪

10:12.800 --> 10:16.000
♪Quietly, I turn into a sky lantern♪

10:16.320 --> 10:19.480
♪To light your way through the night♪

10:19.610 --> 10:21.330
♪Knowing right and wrong♪

10:21.490 --> 10:25.320
♪Black and gray are all illusions♪

10:25.320 --> 10:26.850
No!

10:26.850 --> 10:28.720
♪You're still screaming♪

10:28.880 --> 10:33.240
♪Running relentlessly without regret♪

10:33.440 --> 10:38.090
♪The storm looms, yet the wind stands in its way♪

10:38.920 --> 10:39.970
Xiuyuan!

10:39.970 --> 10:41.290
♪A final farewell left on the cliff♪

10:41.400 --> 10:43.600
♪I'd shatter my soul♪

10:43.880 --> 10:48.560
♪To lay all your days in peace♪

10:48.880 --> 10:50.560
♪Who says that love and hate♪

10:50.960 --> 10:55.680
♪Pain and wounds cannot be stopped?♪

10:55.920 --> 10:57.760
♪I will level the seas and mountains♪

10:58.200 --> 11:02.400
♪Break the waves, no matter how mad it seems♪

11:02.750 --> 11:07.160
♪The storm looms, yet I stand in its way♪

11:07.480 --> 11:10.400
♪Torn inside, still I burn bright♪

11:10.680 --> 11:16.720
♪With the light from my fingertips, I build a paradise♪

11:17.360 --> 11:21.080
♪To wander with you♪

11:26.920 --> 11:27.450
Ye.

11:27.800 --> 11:28.420
How is it?

11:29.400 --> 11:30.260
- Are you okay? - Lu?

11:30.870 --> 11:31.450
Lu?

11:36.680 --> 11:37.260
Gelin?

11:37.560 --> 11:38.850
You talked about forever.

11:39.160 --> 11:40.380
What would I do if you died?

11:41.350 --> 11:41.940
Gelin.

11:42.990 --> 11:43.330
I...

11:43.590 --> 11:44.300
Don't say anything.

11:45.080 --> 11:45.850
Just stay alive.

11:52.160 --> 11:53.330
Look. What is it?

11:55.230 --> 11:56.420
The demonic energy has all been purified by it.

12:09.510 --> 12:10.060
Lifei.

12:11.680 --> 12:12.210
Lifei!

12:13.320 --> 12:13.970
Where are you hurt?

12:17.400 --> 12:18.810
I killed Xiuyuan.

12:20.110 --> 12:21.330
That's Xiuyuan's blood?

12:22.920 --> 12:23.540
Did you...?

12:25.800 --> 12:26.570
What happened?

12:28.110 --> 12:28.970
He's dead.

12:36.320 --> 12:37.210
- Lifei! - Zhaomin.

12:37.510 --> 12:38.300
Calm down.

12:39.080 --> 12:40.090
This isn't your fault.

12:41.470 --> 12:42.260
It's all my fault.

12:44.990 --> 12:46.380
I should be the one dead.

12:46.920 --> 12:47.330
No.

12:47.870 --> 12:48.420
No.

12:49.280 --> 12:50.300
He deserved to die.

12:51.280 --> 12:52.140
He was a demon.

12:53.110 --> 12:54.060
Our enemy.

13:04.040 --> 13:04.780
Zhaomin.

13:07.710 --> 13:08.210
Zhaomin!

13:08.990 --> 13:09.610
Zhaomin!

13:10.350 --> 13:10.970
Zhaomin!

13:11.400 --> 13:11.940
Zhaomin.

13:12.440 --> 13:13.090
Zhaomin!

13:18.470 --> 13:19.180
Who did this?

13:19.750 --> 13:20.850
Who killed Zhaomin?

13:25.870 --> 13:26.810
It was me.

13:33.710 --> 13:34.900
It's all my fault.

13:44.710 --> 13:46.090
The Divine Tree colluded with the Demon Lord

13:46.400 --> 13:47.850
to overthrow the immortal sects.

13:48.350 --> 13:49.060
Seize her!

13:55.750 --> 13:56.330
Your Highness,

13:56.960 --> 13:58.210
what do you mean by this?

13:58.800 --> 13:59.850
She's a demon!

14:10.680 --> 14:12.090
If she hadn't used the Divine Tree's power

14:12.200 --> 14:13.090
to purify the demonic energy,

14:13.830 --> 14:14.690
you would all have been

14:15.280 --> 14:16.570
killed by the demons.

14:17.560 --> 14:18.730
But she is the Divine Tree.

14:19.560 --> 14:20.490
The demon attack

14:20.870 --> 14:21.900
happened because of her.

14:22.400 --> 14:23.540
She's a walking disaster.

14:24.230 --> 14:25.020
Who's the disaster?

14:28.960 --> 14:30.420
Wasn't today's fiasco enough?

14:31.040 --> 14:32.450
If you hadn't coveted the Divine Tree

14:32.560 --> 14:33.610
and insisted on that public trial,

14:34.230 --> 14:36.660
Wuyue Court wouldn't have been caught off guard!

14:37.350 --> 14:37.970
And Elder Guangwei,

14:38.560 --> 14:39.020
Zhaomin,

14:39.350 --> 14:41.140
and so many others wouldn't have...

14:49.800 --> 14:51.020
This demon attack

14:51.560 --> 14:52.810
has severely wounded the immortal sects.

14:53.200 --> 14:54.940
We don't know what the Demon Lord has planned next.

14:55.440 --> 14:56.020
I suggest

14:56.680 --> 14:58.330
you all return

14:58.470 --> 14:59.420
and tend to your wounds.

15:00.110 --> 15:03.380
Don't give the demons another opening.

15:04.960 --> 15:05.610
We'll discuss

15:06.350 --> 15:07.330
everything else later.

15:09.870 --> 15:11.330
Xingzheng Hall was wiped out long ago!

15:11.560 --> 15:12.540
Why should we listen to you?

15:17.350 --> 15:18.730
Everyone, stay still! Behave!

15:27.080 --> 15:28.090
Xingzheng Hall

15:28.560 --> 15:31.420
fell victim to Zong Quan, who colluded with demons.

15:32.110 --> 15:33.020
Though we suffered losses,

15:33.870 --> 15:35.420
we still stand unbroken.

15:36.590 --> 15:39.810
Can't you all learn from that?

15:41.920 --> 15:42.450
Fine.

15:43.040 --> 15:44.090
Defending against the demons matters.

15:44.920 --> 15:46.090
Thank you for the reminder, Your Highness.

15:46.630 --> 15:47.690
We're leaving.

15:48.560 --> 15:49.300
- Go! - Go.

16:11.160 --> 16:15.050
[In Memory of Zhaomin]

16:18.440 --> 16:20.090
Lifei, wake up.

16:22.590 --> 16:24.730
Lifei, wake up!

16:25.470 --> 16:27.490
Carry yourself like a girl.

16:28.080 --> 16:29.140
Be graceful and proper.

16:29.510 --> 16:30.780
No more clumsiness.

16:30.920 --> 16:31.690
Understand?

16:34.560 --> 16:35.300
Lifei.

16:36.990 --> 16:37.730
Take care.

16:48.990 --> 16:49.780
Zhaomin,

16:51.710 --> 16:53.140
I'll listen to you from now on.

16:55.230 --> 16:56.450
Please don't be mad at me.

17:08.360 --> 17:09.580
Zhaomin loved you so much.

17:11.790 --> 17:13.010
She wouldn't be mad at you.

17:18.240 --> 17:20.560
[In Memory of Zhaomin]

17:22.200 --> 17:22.860
Zhaomin.

17:24.960 --> 17:25.660
I bought

17:25.990 --> 17:27.820
these for you in Duanming City.

17:28.990 --> 17:30.820
Peepshow scrolls,

17:31.750 --> 17:32.770
assorted preserved fruits,

17:33.550 --> 17:34.580
and lotus incense.

17:35.840 --> 17:37.450
I always wanted to give them to you.

17:41.400 --> 17:42.940
But I never had the courage.

17:51.310 --> 17:52.580
I'll go check on Master.

18:14.350 --> 18:17.040
[In Memory of Guangwei]

18:20.360 --> 18:22.490
Here, Guangwei.

18:23.510 --> 18:24.140
Drink.

18:32.600 --> 18:33.340
Master,

18:34.160 --> 18:35.770
you're hurt. You shouldn't drink.

18:38.160 --> 18:38.940
Besides,

18:40.200 --> 18:41.450
Elder Guangwei was aloof

18:42.270 --> 18:43.100
and serious.

18:43.880 --> 18:45.180
He probably didn't like wine.

18:45.790 --> 18:47.010
Bring him tea next time.

18:47.400 --> 18:49.820
Since when did you start fussing over people?

18:51.400 --> 18:52.940
You're becoming more and more like Zhaomin.

18:57.030 --> 18:58.250
Did you go see Zhaomin?

19:04.470 --> 19:05.420
If it weren't for saving me,

19:06.790 --> 19:08.180
Zhaomin wouldn't have died.

19:09.310 --> 19:10.050
It's all my fault.

19:11.400 --> 19:12.380
First, Master.

19:14.710 --> 19:16.100
Then Elder Guangwei.

19:17.640 --> 19:18.490
Zhaomin.

19:19.640 --> 19:20.690
And Xiuyuan.

19:21.470 --> 19:23.250
I used to call him a jinx.

19:24.440 --> 19:25.690
Turns out I'm the real jinx.

19:32.960 --> 19:33.580
Alright.

19:34.600 --> 19:35.730
Stop overthinking.

19:37.160 --> 19:38.180
You and Xiuyuan

19:38.680 --> 19:40.380
were both caught up in fate.

19:40.920 --> 19:41.860
Some things

19:42.750 --> 19:43.690
are hard to explain.

19:45.710 --> 19:47.210
But one thing is clear.

19:47.510 --> 19:49.660
They all wanted you to live well.

19:50.960 --> 19:52.420
Don't let them down.

19:54.230 --> 19:55.050
Elder Guangwei?

19:56.270 --> 19:57.690
Was it him who woke Xiuyuan?

20:00.990 --> 20:02.180
Guangwei

20:02.200 --> 20:04.010
used the last of his strength.

20:04.710 --> 20:06.340
He channeled the Heart-Cleansing Art

20:07.030 --> 20:08.250
into Xiuyuan's forehead.

20:09.600 --> 20:10.620
The Heart-Cleansing Art?

20:11.270 --> 20:12.250
It can

20:13.360 --> 20:16.180
dissolve the demon's Soul-Bewitching Vines.

20:16.710 --> 20:18.620
In the last Sea Calamity,

20:18.640 --> 20:19.690
we saw too many of the monsters

20:19.710 --> 20:21.420
infected by those vines.

20:21.990 --> 20:23.290
They lost themselves,

20:23.710 --> 20:24.860
just like Xiuyuan,

20:25.160 --> 20:26.770
and became violent and bloodthirsty.

20:29.120 --> 20:30.380
But you know

20:30.920 --> 20:32.660
that wasn't Xiuyuan's true self.

20:35.550 --> 20:36.340
I know.

20:38.550 --> 20:40.100
But I still killed him.

20:42.710 --> 20:43.450
In that moment,

20:44.270 --> 20:46.180
I gave it everything I had to kill him.

20:48.880 --> 20:50.140
He'd rather die by my hand

20:51.990 --> 20:53.530
than hurt me.

21:01.440 --> 21:03.730
If you're hurting, just cry.

21:04.550 --> 21:06.660
You'll feel better.

21:10.640 --> 21:11.530
Master.

21:13.160 --> 21:14.180
I'm so scared.

21:15.710 --> 21:17.050
I'm afraid of dragging more of you down.

21:19.230 --> 21:21.140
Afraid of watching more people die before me.

21:23.550 --> 21:25.050
I can't take it anymore.

21:26.470 --> 21:27.380
I liked you better

21:27.710 --> 21:29.180
the way you used to be.

21:29.920 --> 21:31.530
You were so carefree.

21:32.840 --> 21:33.730
If you ask me,

21:34.120 --> 21:35.140
life and death are just fate.

21:35.160 --> 21:36.140
Let things take their course.

21:36.470 --> 21:39.050
Don't carry everything on your own shoulders.

21:39.710 --> 21:41.530
The Sea Calamity looms, and human hearts run deep.

21:42.920 --> 21:44.660
You've already severed your worldly ties.

21:45.640 --> 21:46.900
Why not just leave?

21:47.440 --> 21:48.860
Find a place to live in seclusion,

21:49.310 --> 21:50.860
just like Qingcheng.

21:51.440 --> 21:52.450
I believe

21:53.120 --> 21:53.970
there must be a place for you

21:54.750 --> 21:56.380
in this vast world.

21:59.400 --> 22:00.690
I'm the Divine Tree after all.

22:02.230 --> 22:04.140
There's no place for me in this life.

22:23.790 --> 22:24.420
Your Highness.

22:24.600 --> 22:25.210
Mr. Luo.

22:26.710 --> 22:27.690
You're still here?

22:29.200 --> 22:30.860
I'm worried about the safety of the immortal sects.

22:30.880 --> 22:31.900
I can neither eat nor sleep.

22:32.120 --> 22:32.970
After much thought,

22:33.070 --> 22:34.180
I'd like to share

22:34.400 --> 22:35.900
some honest words with you.

22:37.680 --> 22:38.450
Mr. Luo, go on.

22:40.880 --> 22:41.900
After the battle at Wuyue Court,

22:42.030 --> 22:43.250
the immortal sects are badly weakened

22:43.440 --> 22:44.380
and divided.

22:44.510 --> 22:45.970
They're in no shape to fight the demons again.

22:46.400 --> 22:48.580
But your influence is at its peak.

22:49.030 --> 22:51.290
And the Divine Tree trusts you completely.

22:51.710 --> 22:52.490
I believe

22:52.750 --> 22:54.940
you could use the Divine Tree to command the world.

22:55.400 --> 22:58.860
Lifei is the disciple of Elder Qingcheng and Elder Chongyi,

22:59.640 --> 23:01.530
and my closest friend.

23:02.160 --> 23:04.380
Anyone who schemes against her or tries to harm her

23:05.360 --> 23:07.140
is my enemy.

23:08.120 --> 23:09.010
No matter who they are,

23:09.400 --> 23:10.730
I will slaughter their entire clan

23:11.400 --> 23:12.340
to the very last.

23:15.200 --> 23:16.730
Guess I spoke out of turn.

23:17.470 --> 23:18.290
Alright then.

23:18.790 --> 23:19.490
I'm leaving.

23:19.640 --> 23:20.290
See yourself out.

23:30.640 --> 23:31.970
Ungrateful fool.

23:32.400 --> 23:33.580
I offer you good counsel,

23:33.600 --> 23:34.490
and you reject it.

23:35.400 --> 23:36.770
If I weren't wounded,

23:36.790 --> 23:38.250
you'd never get to claim the Divine Tree

23:38.360 --> 23:39.580
and lord it over me.

23:40.230 --> 23:40.730
Who's there?

23:44.600 --> 23:45.530
You?

23:50.550 --> 23:52.340
Patrols must be tightened this time.

23:52.790 --> 23:53.940
If the Divine Tree appears,

23:54.310 --> 23:55.580
capture it alive.

23:56.360 --> 23:57.140
Go patrol.

23:59.470 --> 24:00.010
Guardian,

24:00.470 --> 24:01.340
has the Lord awakened?

24:04.360 --> 24:05.180
Why isn't he awake yet?

24:08.200 --> 24:09.490
Everyone is waiting.

24:10.120 --> 24:10.940
If he never wakes up...

24:10.960 --> 24:11.620
Qiongqi!

24:14.470 --> 24:15.180
Guardian,

24:15.510 --> 24:16.730
we've lain low for centuries.

24:16.880 --> 24:18.180
We've come so far.

24:18.790 --> 24:20.050
We have to have a backup plan.

24:20.230 --> 24:21.050
Think of all our people.

24:21.230 --> 24:22.050
Are we supposed to

24:22.070 --> 24:23.340
just wait here forever?

24:25.400 --> 24:26.620
If the Lord hadn't been too soft

24:27.270 --> 24:28.420
to absorb the Divine Tree,

24:28.920 --> 24:29.690
it wouldn't have come to this.

24:29.710 --> 24:30.340
Silence!

24:32.160 --> 24:33.820
The Lord will not die.

24:34.230 --> 24:34.860
Yes.

24:35.270 --> 24:36.530
The Lord is the supreme ruler of our clan.

24:36.990 --> 24:38.820
He'll never be defeated by those petty immortals!

25:02.400 --> 25:03.940
He's a little demon.

25:04.310 --> 25:06.250
I need to kill him!

25:08.070 --> 25:08.820
Even if he's the Demon Lord,

25:09.510 --> 25:10.530
he's still a life.

25:14.550 --> 25:15.210
Besides,

25:15.880 --> 25:17.340
he's returned to his original state now.

25:18.470 --> 25:19.940
There's no good or evil in him.

25:26.070 --> 25:26.530
Here.

25:28.120 --> 25:29.250
You won't eat radish porridge.

25:29.680 --> 25:30.620
And you spit out the sweet potato.

25:31.070 --> 25:33.180
This is milk I stole

25:33.200 --> 25:34.380
from that tiger.

25:34.680 --> 25:35.380
Just try a little.

25:40.360 --> 25:41.770
What do you even want?

25:54.400 --> 25:55.250
You two...

25:57.600 --> 25:59.380
You two were meant to be together.

26:07.160 --> 26:07.730
Master,

26:07.920 --> 26:09.770
why hasn't he grown

26:09.790 --> 26:11.140
in all these centuries?

26:11.550 --> 26:12.660
[Young Hu Jiaping]
Is he some kind of monster?

26:14.310 --> 26:15.010
Don't talk nonsense.

26:15.400 --> 26:15.860
Go.

26:15.960 --> 26:17.860
Deliver this letter to Chufeng Academy.

26:23.680 --> 26:24.940
Resentment is a net,

26:26.230 --> 26:27.490
trapping both user and prey.

26:28.710 --> 26:29.970
Only by breaking free

26:30.360 --> 26:31.860
can the soul find peace.

26:41.510 --> 26:42.690
Graceful as bamboo,

26:42.920 --> 26:43.900
virtue known afar.

26:44.470 --> 26:45.140
From now on,

26:45.550 --> 26:47.530
your name will be Lei Xiuyuan.

26:49.960 --> 26:50.380
Here.

26:50.600 --> 26:51.690
Pay your respects to the Crown Prince.

26:53.030 --> 26:54.900
Greetings, Your Royal Highness.

26:56.310 --> 26:57.140
No need for formalities.

26:57.710 --> 26:58.490
My name is Ye Ye.

26:58.600 --> 27:00.340
Let's study and play together

27:00.360 --> 27:01.100
from now on.

27:12.960 --> 27:13.690
No way?

27:14.510 --> 27:15.900
Me? Acting Sect Leader?

27:16.440 --> 27:18.050
We old ones are either wounded

27:18.550 --> 27:19.250
or broken.

27:19.680 --> 27:21.940
You younger ones are either too badly hurt

27:21.990 --> 27:23.380
or still too inexperienced.

27:25.990 --> 27:26.660
So,

27:27.030 --> 27:28.380
you are

27:28.710 --> 27:29.860
the best choice.

27:29.960 --> 27:31.970
I'm the worst choice.

27:33.640 --> 27:34.210
Sir,

27:34.600 --> 27:35.770
you know me.

27:35.990 --> 27:36.820
I... I'm

27:37.120 --> 27:38.050
naturally lazy.

27:38.510 --> 27:39.490
I really can't do it.

27:41.470 --> 27:42.380
You think

27:42.710 --> 27:43.770
you're lazier than me?

27:43.990 --> 27:45.050
You want to talk about being lazy?

27:45.960 --> 27:47.290
You have a strong sense of right and wrong.

27:47.710 --> 27:49.250
You're chivalrous and courageous.

27:49.990 --> 27:51.580
You don't follow the crowd.

27:53.230 --> 27:55.290
That's more than enough.

27:56.270 --> 27:57.820
We trust you

27:58.400 --> 27:59.340
to be the acting Sect Leader.

27:59.400 --> 28:00.690
This is wrong.

28:03.030 --> 28:03.940
Xiguang.

28:04.680 --> 28:05.420
Master.

28:06.310 --> 28:08.380
It's our fault.

28:09.200 --> 28:10.820
At the critical moment,

28:11.270 --> 28:12.690
we're all too wounded and weak

28:12.710 --> 28:13.860
to take care of ourselves.

28:14.360 --> 28:16.100
We have no choice but to place this heavy burden

28:17.120 --> 28:18.730
on you.

28:19.510 --> 28:20.100
Master!

28:20.550 --> 28:21.940
Please. I can't accept this.

28:22.230 --> 28:22.730
Master.

28:23.230 --> 28:23.730
Master.

28:24.310 --> 28:25.490
I'm not capable enough.

28:26.360 --> 28:27.340
I'm ashamed.

28:27.880 --> 28:28.620
Ma'am.

28:29.270 --> 28:29.900
Master.

28:30.360 --> 28:31.340
Don't say that.

28:32.440 --> 28:33.580
I've been a terrible disciple.

28:34.030 --> 28:36.010
It's easy

28:36.030 --> 28:36.820
to change that.

28:37.440 --> 28:38.290
Just agree to be

28:38.640 --> 28:39.530
the acting Sect Leader.

28:41.790 --> 28:42.380
Alright.

28:42.840 --> 28:45.970
I'll notify everyone as soon as possible.

28:47.680 --> 28:48.580
Do a good job.

29:03.310 --> 29:03.940
Zhaomin,

29:04.920 --> 29:07.730
I never thought the nightmare I had on Fanghu Island would come true.

29:08.360 --> 29:10.860
They actually want me to be acting Sect Leader.

29:11.310 --> 29:11.730
I...

29:13.880 --> 29:15.380
It's not that I'm scared.

29:15.750 --> 29:16.140
I...

29:19.160 --> 29:20.490
Fine. I'm just scared.

29:21.440 --> 29:23.620
I'm afraid I won't do a good job.

29:24.270 --> 29:25.340
You know me.

29:26.070 --> 29:27.820
I'm a free spirit.

29:27.840 --> 29:30.420
I can't handle this kind of responsibility.

29:34.270 --> 29:35.730
I have no choice now.

29:36.400 --> 29:38.210
I'm planning to sneak down the mountain tonight.

29:38.230 --> 29:39.380
I'll run far away.

29:39.990 --> 29:41.940
Let them find another disciple for this position.

29:46.160 --> 29:48.380
I thought you'd be reliable in a crisis.

29:49.880 --> 29:51.770
Never expected you to disappoint me so much!

30:02.200 --> 30:02.970
If you run,

30:03.360 --> 30:04.860
who will protect Lifei, Simo,

30:04.880 --> 30:06.140
and the other juniors?

30:06.680 --> 30:09.050
Who will look after the injured elders?

30:10.360 --> 30:11.010
Xiguang,

30:11.790 --> 30:13.380
you've run away once before.

30:14.230 --> 30:15.100
Don't run

30:15.360 --> 30:16.970
and hide again this time.

30:25.270 --> 30:25.820
Zhao...

30:35.550 --> 30:36.380
Zhaomin!

30:37.310 --> 30:38.290
Don't worry!

30:41.030 --> 30:41.940
I'll take good care of them

30:43.710 --> 30:44.620
for you.

30:48.640 --> 30:50.010
Deng may seem unreliable,

30:50.680 --> 30:51.770
but he's thoughtful,

30:51.990 --> 30:52.900
honorable,

30:53.160 --> 30:54.010
and far better than most.

30:54.960 --> 30:56.010
Wuyue Court will thrive

30:56.400 --> 30:57.490
under his leadership.

30:59.550 --> 31:00.770
You seem to be in better spirits

31:01.270 --> 31:02.380
these past few days.

31:05.440 --> 31:06.450
Staying a broken mess

31:07.200 --> 31:08.420
would only worry Master

31:08.750 --> 31:09.690
and everyone else.

31:11.160 --> 31:12.290
I don't want to be a burden.

31:14.790 --> 31:15.940
Being with you is a blessing,

31:16.360 --> 31:17.530
if anything.

31:21.360 --> 31:21.940
Lifei.

31:22.790 --> 31:23.530
I know

31:24.070 --> 31:25.580
you've been grieving over Xiuyuan.

31:27.230 --> 31:27.900
But

31:28.510 --> 31:29.580
Rakshasa took him away.

31:30.360 --> 31:31.820
Maybe he's still alive.

31:47.550 --> 31:49.180
The Fragrance Bond is gone.

31:51.120 --> 31:52.420
He's really not here anymore.

32:02.230 --> 32:02.770
Lifei.

32:03.790 --> 32:04.380
Let the past

32:04.600 --> 32:05.250
stay in the past.

32:06.120 --> 32:07.180
Think about the people

32:07.790 --> 32:09.100
still by your side.

32:13.120 --> 32:13.620
Oh,

32:14.270 --> 32:15.250
how's Ye Ye?

32:15.710 --> 32:17.900
He was badly hurt saving me that day.

32:19.790 --> 32:21.140
I haven't seen him in days.

32:21.710 --> 32:22.620
Wasn't he taken away

32:22.990 --> 32:24.180
by Sect Leader Miao?

32:25.680 --> 32:27.690
Changyue and Ye Ye wouldn't just leave without a word.

32:28.400 --> 32:29.490
Could something have happened?

32:30.710 --> 32:31.580
Don't panic.

32:32.310 --> 32:34.100
Maybe he was wounded and unconscious,

32:34.440 --> 32:36.010
and the Dizang Sect disciples took him back.

32:36.470 --> 32:37.210
I'll send someone to ask.

32:37.680 --> 32:38.140
Alright.

32:46.200 --> 32:46.860
Lifei,

32:47.230 --> 32:48.100
Master said you need to

32:48.270 --> 32:48.970
drink this medicine.

32:50.550 --> 32:51.450
Thanks.

32:52.960 --> 32:54.450
I haven't seen Master all afternoon.

32:54.880 --> 32:55.770
Where did he go?

32:56.400 --> 32:57.900
He went to Hushe Peak.

33:35.790 --> 33:37.380
The horn of the Si beast.
[*Divine one-horned animal]

33:40.510 --> 33:41.250
Master!

33:46.070 --> 33:46.690
Master.

33:47.710 --> 33:48.770
What are you doing here?

33:50.840 --> 33:51.770
I want to

33:52.360 --> 33:53.620
fix this place up.

33:54.360 --> 33:55.900
Look how messy it is.

33:58.030 --> 33:58.820
Let me do it.

34:00.200 --> 34:01.450
Back in Qingqiu,

34:01.750 --> 34:03.860
the little cabin often got battered by the wind.

34:04.270 --> 34:05.290
I was always the one fixing it.

34:07.640 --> 34:09.290
I can't believe Qingcheng

34:09.880 --> 34:12.050
made you do all that work.

34:15.630 --> 34:16.260
Sit down.

34:20.070 --> 34:21.090
That's nothing.

34:22.190 --> 34:23.970
That old man had all sorts of quirks.

34:24.760 --> 34:26.090
He bragged without blinking an eye.

34:26.590 --> 34:28.650
He lost nearly every time he gambled.

34:29.990 --> 34:31.420
Stingy and greedy.

34:31.960 --> 34:33.820
All day he just lay in his chair,

34:34.110 --> 34:35.380
smoking and dozing off.

34:35.720 --> 34:36.860
He was lazy

34:37.240 --> 34:38.530
and picky about everything.

34:39.760 --> 34:41.570
It was always something, like the radish being too bland

34:41.800 --> 34:43.220
or the tea being too hot.

34:44.840 --> 34:45.650
He...

34:49.920 --> 34:50.570
But

34:52.150 --> 34:54.220
our days were always so joyful

34:55.190 --> 34:56.130
and lively.

34:56.630 --> 34:57.650
We lived better than immortals.

35:00.110 --> 35:03.380
All these years, Qingcheng had you by his side.

35:04.720 --> 35:07.260
That's why he got to live such a happy life.

35:09.590 --> 35:11.010
I should thank you for him.

35:19.070 --> 35:20.420
I'm the one who owes him.

35:23.150 --> 35:24.450
He did so much for me.

35:25.720 --> 35:27.130
But I never gave anything back.

35:28.030 --> 35:29.090
What are you saying?

35:29.840 --> 35:31.260
You gave plenty.

35:31.510 --> 35:32.860
He ate so much of your delicious cooking

35:32.880 --> 35:34.010
over the years.

35:36.280 --> 35:37.650
Simo is always talking

35:38.240 --> 35:40.450
about your chicken and mushroom stew.

35:42.440 --> 35:43.860
Have you seen

35:43.880 --> 35:44.820
Simo lately?

35:46.070 --> 35:46.780
No.

35:48.280 --> 35:49.340
Simo's missing?

35:49.720 --> 35:50.780
Haven't seen him lately.

35:54.150 --> 35:55.610
Well, Master,

35:55.920 --> 35:56.940
I'll fix the cabin.

35:57.880 --> 35:58.900
You're still hurt.

35:59.400 --> 36:00.490
Get some rest.

36:00.960 --> 36:01.780
I'll be back soon.

36:11.470 --> 36:12.490
Leaving already?

36:17.760 --> 36:18.940
Qingcheng,

36:20.590 --> 36:23.570
Lifei really takes after you.

36:35.510 --> 36:36.170
Qingcheng.

36:37.280 --> 36:40.450
That kid's still as mischievous as ever.

37:23.670 --> 37:24.530
Qingcheng, Guangwei.

37:26.720 --> 37:31.260
The child you two fought so hard to protect...

37:40.320 --> 37:41.090
I hope...

37:43.670 --> 37:48.650
I hope she has fewer hardships ahead.

37:55.840 --> 37:56.570
I asked the guards.

37:57.030 --> 37:58.010
When the demons retreated,

37:58.400 --> 37:59.130
Ye Ye and Simo

37:59.150 --> 38:00.610
went after them.

38:01.240 --> 38:01.970
They haven't come back.

38:02.880 --> 38:03.970
That was days ago.

38:04.760 --> 38:05.900
Could the demons have found them?

38:08.070 --> 38:09.420
Ye Ye carried a message talisman.

38:09.630 --> 38:10.700
If anything had happened,

38:10.880 --> 38:12.050
he would've let us know.

38:12.990 --> 38:14.090
Since we haven't heard anything,

38:14.510 --> 38:16.130
they probably haven't found the demons yet.

38:19.720 --> 38:20.700
Demons are vicious.

38:21.550 --> 38:22.650
Better if they don't find them.

38:23.360 --> 38:24.530
Zhaomin is already gone.

38:25.030 --> 38:26.090
If Simo and the others...

38:27.960 --> 38:29.220
I've already sent people to search.

38:29.470 --> 38:30.780
We'll hear something soon.

38:33.510 --> 38:34.420
I'll go look again.

38:58.990 --> 38:59.740
My Lord.

39:02.510 --> 39:03.260
My Lord.

39:06.960 --> 39:08.700
Your old friends followed us here.

39:09.400 --> 39:11.220
Qiongqi is entertaining them.

39:15.760 --> 39:17.450
It's been seven full days.

39:17.920 --> 39:20.050
My Lord, when will you wake up?

39:23.990 --> 39:24.780
I know

39:26.280 --> 39:28.970
the last person you want to hurt is Jiang Lifei.

39:32.360 --> 39:34.420
I'll bring her to you.

39:39.190 --> 39:40.420
Any news from your side?

39:42.190 --> 39:43.570
The disciples I sent haven't reported back.

39:43.590 --> 39:44.820
We can't find Ye Ye

39:44.960 --> 39:45.970
or the others either.

39:46.110 --> 39:46.970
Where could they have gone?

39:46.990 --> 39:47.420
Wait.

39:47.800 --> 39:48.490
There's demonic energy.

39:59.670 --> 40:00.860
It's Ye Ye and the others' swords.

40:02.590 --> 40:04.700
If you don't want Ye Ye and his two companions to die,

40:05.400 --> 40:06.610
trade Jiang Lifei for them

40:07.110 --> 40:08.340
tomorrow at Chen hour

40:09.030 --> 40:10.820
outside Lilie Valley.

40:12.670 --> 40:13.820
So they're there.

40:14.960 --> 40:15.610
I'm going now.

40:16.590 --> 40:17.260
Don't rush.

40:18.550 --> 40:19.610
Demons are cunning and treacherous.

40:20.030 --> 40:21.420
This could be a trap.

40:23.360 --> 40:23.940
You're right.

40:24.400 --> 40:24.970
Alright then.

40:25.880 --> 40:27.050
I'll go scout things out.

40:27.590 --> 40:28.260
Everyone else

40:28.510 --> 40:29.260
stays put.

40:30.880 --> 40:31.380
And

40:31.990 --> 40:33.450
don't tell Jiang Lifei.

41:03.150 --> 41:03.700
Excuse me.

41:04.470 --> 41:05.570
Where can I find Deng?

41:05.590 --> 41:06.780
She got so many disciples killed.

41:07.070 --> 41:07.820
How dare she show up?

41:08.030 --> 41:08.900
She's not even human.

41:09.510 --> 41:10.050
What a plague.

41:10.400 --> 41:10.900
Let's go.

41:22.630 --> 41:24.300
Your Highness, your internal injuries haven't healed.

41:24.470 --> 41:25.740
Don't go to Lilie Valley.

41:27.920 --> 41:28.450
Tongzhou.

41:29.280 --> 41:30.490
Did you find Ye Ye and the others?

41:31.280 --> 41:32.420
Are they in Lilie Valley?

41:33.070 --> 41:34.260
Someone spotted them nearby.

41:34.800 --> 41:36.130
Deng Xiguang has already gone to check.

41:36.800 --> 41:37.700
Then I need to go too.

41:41.880 --> 41:42.610
What's wrong?

41:43.720 --> 41:44.610
Old injury flaring up?

41:45.630 --> 41:46.650
You need to be careful.

41:47.150 --> 41:47.780
Let me see.

41:49.280 --> 41:49.900
I'm fine.

42:12.280 --> 42:12.940
Sorry.

42:13.840 --> 42:15.090
I have to get stronger

42:15.800 --> 42:16.940
to protect you.

42:20.190 --> 42:20.940
Come here.

42:24.590 --> 42:25.170
Your Highness!

42:31.440 --> 42:32.940
Your spirit energy came from Lifei.

42:34.190 --> 42:35.420
Only by drawing on her spirit energy

42:36.440 --> 42:37.450
can you help me.

42:42.050 --> 42:42.780
[The Eternal Fragrance]

42:42.780 --> 42:44.560
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

42:57.500 --> 43:01.020
♪The warmth within my arms♪

43:01.180 --> 43:04.700
♪I can no longer hold on to♪

43:04.820 --> 43:08.340
♪In the cold night, how can I♪

43:08.460 --> 43:11.940
♪Keep you warm until sunrise?♪

43:11.940 --> 43:15.580
♪My heartbeat freezes♪

43:15.980 --> 43:19.260
♪I can no longer tell you♪

43:19.380 --> 43:22.900
♪Looking you in the eyes, I cannot♪

43:22.940 --> 43:25.940
♪Utter that line♪

43:26.100 --> 43:28.140
♪Knowing love and hate♪

43:28.220 --> 43:32.620
♪Pain and wounds cannot be stopped♪

43:33.340 --> 43:35.420
♪I still linger on♪

43:35.580 --> 43:39.860
♪Unwilling to let go of every inch of our past♪

43:40.020 --> 43:44.540
♪Last night's stars cast faint glimmers♪

43:44.620 --> 43:48.140
♪But we thought nothing of it♪

43:48.220 --> 43:51.660
♪With a heartbroken cry♪

43:51.940 --> 43:55.180
♪I wish you well♪

43:55.340 --> 43:57.060
♪Knowing right and wrong♪

43:57.220 --> 44:01.900
♪Black and gray are all illusions♪

44:02.500 --> 44:04.580
♪You're still screaming♪

44:04.740 --> 44:09.220
♪Running relentlessly without regret♪

44:09.340 --> 44:13.820
♪The storm looms, yet the wind stands in its way♪

44:14.060 --> 44:17.020
♪A final farewell left on the cliff♪

44:17.140 --> 44:19.020
♪Leaping straight into♪

44:19.140 --> 44:23.900
♪That heartbreaking past♪

44:24.140 --> 44:27.660
♪Just to keep you safe♪

44:34.100 --> 44:37.420
♪My breath is about to stop♪

44:37.540 --> 44:41.060
♪Those hands can no longer hold yours♪

44:41.180 --> 44:44.620
♪Through the future snow, wind, and fog♪

44:44.780 --> 44:47.980
♪Who will be there by your side?♪

44:48.100 --> 44:51.820
♪I smile as it ends♪

44:51.980 --> 44:55.620
♪Afraid that you might cry for me♪

44:55.820 --> 44:59.220
♪Quietly, I turn into a sky lantern♪

44:59.380 --> 45:02.500
♪To light your way through the night♪

45:02.580 --> 45:04.620
♪Knowing love and hate♪

45:04.700 --> 45:09.100
♪Pain and wounds cannot be stopped♪

45:09.860 --> 45:11.900
♪I still linger on♪

45:12.060 --> 45:16.340
♪Unwilling to let go of every inch of our past♪

45:16.500 --> 45:21.020
♪The storm looms, yet I stand in its way♪

45:21.100 --> 45:24.300
♪Torn inside, still I burn bright♪

45:24.500 --> 45:26.460
♪With the light from my fingertips♪

45:26.540 --> 45:30.940
♪I build a paradise♪

45:31.100 --> 45:34.580
♪To wander with you♪
